name: Streadata.io API Gallery - School Digger
description: This is a repository of school digger APIs, self-contained as a Github repository, with HTML and YAML representations of the APIs and their surrounding operations.

apis.name: School Digger
apis.description: Start your search for a great school at SchoolDigger.com! We have test scores, rankings, school and district boundaries, student/teacher ratios, ethnic makeup, and scores of other useful metrics and information for over 120,000 elementary, middle, and high schools in the United States!
